	('A_yZiqT0Cz7sO6zt4oRxe', 'Lost Cat of Aerathiel', 'https://utfs.io/f/2b8381d8-46c0-4de5-9ca8-0631c54aacc6-1vufp.jpg', '<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/vVncoiH.jpeg\" alt=\"alt\">\n<center><p>Hello Ninja! I have another urgent request! It seems my mischievous cat has run away.. again! Usually, he comes home by now and he hasn\'t appeared to the sound of his favorite treats rattling at the gates. I can\'t help to think he left for good.. could you please search for him and bring him back? Oh, I know! Do this favor for me and I will make you a special batch of my Moon Pies! If I had to guess he is probably around Shroud.</p><br></center>\n\n', 'Successfully Delivered Cat to Monami! You decide to leave out the details and actions of the rogue villagers as they no longer exist. \"My cat!! Thank you so much! I hope he didn\'t cause you too much trouble chasing him! I\'ll have to keep him inside from now on\".\n', 'D', 1, NULL, 'all_time', 'event', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 500, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [\"FPPfHAAHWANWlpAvnt2os\"], \"reward_money\": 25000, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"reward_clanpoints\": 0}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"i4uRqn9ofI3sqf_TA-V5a\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/2b8381d8-46c0-4de5-9ca8-0631c54aacc6-1vufp.jpg\", \"sector\": 211, \"latitude\": 10, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 7, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"You recall Monami stating her cat might be located around Shroud.\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": false, \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"attackers_chance\": 0, \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"A7ePbPx0PPSuloy-5qluU\", \"task\": \"collect_item\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.