	('Ha_4NVImmACLTSfni5ur0', 'Rescue Lady Luna', 'https://utfs.io/f/c9878759-7005-497d-8187-b7aa12ce3e5c-aa26we.webp', '<p>To the noble shinobi and esteemed Global ANBU,</p><br><br>\n\n<p>My heart is heavy as I write this. My daughter, Lady Luna, has been taken from me by a ruthless group known as the Shrouded Serpents. They struck in the dead of night, leaving no trace but their demands—a ransom I cannot hope to gather in time. My daughter’s life hangs in the balance, and I turn to you, the protectors of Seichi, for aid.</p><br>\n\n<p>I beg of you, find Lady Luna and bring her back to me. The Serpents are cunning and dangerous, but I trust in your skill and honor. Time is of the essence, and I fear what they may do if their demands are not met. Please, save my daughter. I will owe you a debt that can never be repaid.</p><br>\n\n<p>May the strength of the gods guide you on this perilous mission.</p>\n<p>— The Feudal Lord of Seichi</p><br>', '<p>With the last of the Shrouded Serpents defeated, silence falls over the fortress. You free Lady Luna, who clings to you with relief. The journey back is long, but the sight of the Feudal Lord’s stronghold brings hope. He embraces his daughter, thanking you with deep gratitude. Lady Luna offers a soft smile before retreating to safety. You leave with honor, knowing your bravery has saved a life and secured your place in Seichi\'s legends.</p>', 'D', 1, NULL, 'all_time', 'event', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 150, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 1000, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"reward_clanpoints\": 0}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"A6kJanf_B4TNLzHV7cgFH\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/c9878759-7005-497d-8187-b7aa12ce3e5c-aa26we.webp\", \"sector\": 222, \"latitude\": 1, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 2, \"reward_exp\": 35, \"description\": \"Talk to the Feudal Lord\", \"reward_