	('haIUe77fyIknJZPjCpaJd', 'The Serpent King\'s Mediallion', 'https://utfs.io/f/663874aa-7f39-48e5-839b-534d41b9eeae-jyhx5m.jpg', '<p>As you step onto the shores of Wake Island, you are greeted by the\nmembers of the Global ANBU. Their faces are etched with concern, and\nthey speak in hushed tones of a formidable threat that has been\ntormenting the village of Shroud. A beast, said to be a serpent of\nancient legend, has been wreaking havoc. The creature\'s chakra is seen\nto resonate with the dark, primordial power of the Serpent King from\nthe Elden era.</p>\n\n<p>The ANBU reveals that the last heir of the revered bloodline\n<b>Vengeance of the Serpent King</b>, Haruto, remains in Shroud. His\nmother, Fuwuari, who was the guardian of their lineage, has recently \npassed away, leaving the ancient heritage in a precarious state. It is\nimperative that you travel to the outskirts of Shroud and seek out Haruto. He may hold\nvital knowledge about the nature of the beast or the reasons behind its\nassault on the village.</p>\n', 'You have restored the peace in Shroud.', 'D', 1, NULL, 'all_time', 'event', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 254, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 25000, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 300, \"reward_prestige\": 300, \"reward_clanpoints\": 200}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"2_meZEPmsZeJqTU2iR5i6\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/663874aa-7f39-48e5-839b-534d41b9eeae-jyhx5m.jpg\", \"sector\": 253, \"latitude\": 0, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 1, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"Seek out Haruto near Shroud\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": true, \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"attackers_chance\": 0, \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"You arrive at the mist-shrouded Spirit Lagoon, where Haruto