	('he41-nhtjXmJ-Ujy0xzka', 'Web of Shadows', 'https://utfs.io/f/43446c3a-6c93-4899-968f-669b7bdc8f64-muuytl.jpg', '<p>Recent attacks on supply convoys between Tsukimori and Shine have severely disrupted vital trade routes. The precision and coordination of these ambushes suggest a skilled and organized force at work.<br>Concerned by the escalating threat, the Global ANBU dispatched an operative to investigate, but no word has been received.</p>\n<br><br>\n<p>Now, the Global ANBU tasks you with uncovering the truth behind these attacks and determining the fate of the missing operative.<br>The path ahead is fraught with danger, as dark forces weave their web in the shadows.</p>\n\n', 'The Global ANBU thanks you for your efforts. In the recovered supplies, you find a unique kunai called \"Widow\'s Bite.\" But is this truly the end?', 'D', 1, NULL, 'all_time', 'event', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 500, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [\"8ThTs6ASxHi8UdtXWoAGC\"], \"reward_money\": 7000, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 100, \"reward_prestige\": 100, \"reward_clanpoints\": 20}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"dBDMSLPdJUSoZNp3tDlOq\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/43446c3a-6c93-4899-968f-669b7bdc8f64-muuytl.jpg\", \"sector\": 300, \"latitude\": 0, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 18, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": true, \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"attackers_chance\": 0, \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"476WfX4jZKbLeg_2QP0J8\", \"task\": \"collect_item\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/5a8eaedf-0dd9-4cf3-b111-7cc9aefe351c-bv5rc6.jpg\", \"sector\": 300, \"latitude\": 4, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"item_name\": \"Broken Cart\", \"longitude