	('NHgR5va5YWGh8K1ExFr6B', 'Battle Tower: Prelude to Momo', 'https://utfs.io/f/07d57cce-5e00-4aa0-ac2a-64526af6aa18-1wk931.webp', 'In the hidden depths of Seichi, amidst the shadows of ancient forests and the eerie silence of forgotten ruins, a mysterious yokai demon resides, known as the Enenra. This elusive creature is made of smoke and darkness, an embodiment of nightmares and whispers. The Enenra is said to only reveal itself to those who are pure of heart or those who possess immense spiritual power. Once seen, the Enenra engulfs its victim in a swirling mist of fear and despair, leading them to the brink of insanity before disappearing into the void.<br><br>\n\nLegends within Seichi\'s villages, particularly in the territories of Shroud and Silence, speak of encounters with this demon. In the Misty Morass, where the constant rain nourishes both mystical plants and enigmatic creatures, the Enenra lurks, blending seamlessly with the perpetual fog. Many villagers believe the Enenra is a manifestation of Susanoo\'s storms, a guardian of the sacred land cursed to wander the mists forever.<br><br>\n\nHowever, others claim that the Enenra is a remnant of the ancient wars that ravaged Seichi, a being born from the despair and hatred of those who perished in battle. It is drawn to areas of great conflict, feeding off the lingering negative emotions. To combat the Enenra, only the most skilled shinobi, with deep knowledge of both ninjutsu and spiritual arts, can hope to purify it and prevent it from consuming more souls.<br><br>\n\nThis yokai remains an enigma, a shadowy presence that haunts the darkest corners of Seichi, a reminder of the delicate balance between the physical and spiritual realms. Those who seek it out do so at their peril, for once the Enenra marks you, escape is nearly impossible.<br><br>', NULL, 'D', 1, NULL, 'all_time', 'event', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 5000, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 50000, \"reward_b