	('NO9aTvhLL-SPlOvv0_H_y', 'The Haunting of the Fortune Mountains', 'https://utfs.io/f/047ad577-dad2-4d18-abd5-894ae488d4e5-x9e98h.jpg', '<p>A foreboding alert has circulated through the villages of Seichi, warning of malevolent entities haunting the peaks of the Fortune Mountains. Local villagers and travelers have reported eerie encounters with spirits that defy reason and nature. Among these reports, an old wanderer—an eccentric hermit known for his cryptic sayings—left a riddle at the base of the mountains, scrawled on ancient parchment. It reads:</p><br><br>\n\n<center><i>\"In the shadows of the Fortune\'s peak, three spirits hide,<br>One thirsts for the crimson tide, its hunger won\'t subside.<br>Another preys on dreams, turning hope into despair,<br>While the third seeks peace, but in darkness it does fare.<br>Solve their desires, and bring the night to light.\"</i></center><br><br>\n\n<p>The Global ANBU, having received this strange riddle along with the alert, have issued a mission for skilled shinobi to decipher the clues, confront these apparitions, and cleanse the area before they bring further harm to the region.</p>\n\n', 'Congratulations, brave shinobi! You have successfully cleansed the Fortune Mountains of the malevolent entities that haunted its peaks. ', 'D', 1, NULL, 'all_time', 'event', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 200, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 15000, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"reward_prestige\": 150, \"reward_clanpoints\": 0}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"ioMj6bhp0NV-JwZ8RwXzd\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/047ad577-dad2-4d18-abd5-894ae488d4e5-x9e98h.jpg\", \"sector\": 296, \"latitude\": 1, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 1, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": false, \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \