	('O7lZSbfKW1E5Ohwtvugs-', 'The Path to Current', 'https://utfs.io/f/224dfa09-b46d-4410-a691-0f2e567d8dcc-fkgz38.webp', 'Welcome, traveler, to the village of Current, where the winds of Fujin shape the lives and destiny of its people. The history here is one of resilience and harmony with the elements. To truly understand the essence of Current, you must trace the steps of the first settlers, from their initial settlement near Konoki to the discovery of Whirling Valley. Join me in uncovering the story of this remarkable place.<br><br>\n\nStart your journey at Oakwood Forest, rich in resources but eventually too confining for the pioneering settlers. Though it provided abundantly, the dense forest felt confining, prompting them to seek a more open and wind-swept land.<br><br>\n\nContinue to the Southern Windswept Grassland, where the settlers first felt the liberating winds that would become central to their new life.As they moved into the open grasslands, the settlers felt the freedom and potential of the wind, a force that would soon define their existence.<br><br>\n\nProceed to the Northern Windswept Grassland, where the settlers continued their journey through the open plains, guided by the ever-present wind.<br><br>\n\nMake your way to Tornado Valley, a place where the winds grow fierce and formidable, testing the resilience of the settlers.<br><br>\n\nFinally, arrive at Whirling Valley, the heart of Current. Here, the settlers founded the village of Current, embracing the winds that would shape their lives. Here, the shrine to Fujin still stands, a testament to their respect and reverence for the wind.<br><br>\n', 'Congratulations, shinobi! You\'ve completed your mission in Current, exploring its rich history. Starting at Oakwood Forest, you traced settlers’ paths and felt the liberating winds of Southern Windswept Grassland. Your journey through Northern Windswept Grassland and Tornado Valley tested your resilience. In Whirling Valley, you witnessed the village’s founding and Fujin\'s shrine. Your dedication honors Current\'s past. Well done! — Tenjiro Sensei', 'D', 1, NULL, 'all_time', 'event', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 0, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [\"1rOv-F4_-DXXT6YNlqi05\"], \"reward_money\": 1000, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"reward_clanpoints\": 0}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"Nojz80xMOioO6pQ6UAyrl\", \"task\": \"defeat_opponents\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/96fdbdc2-3014-4480-acdd-f4548925dee8-wmap2w.webp\", \"sector\": 308, \"latitude\": 5, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 16, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"scaleGains\": 1, \"description\": \"\", \"opponent_ai\": \"Zp0PnhIagkMf-2jyi5NbB\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": false, \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"opponent_name\": \"Furuki no Seirei\", \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"drawDescription\": \"The battle ended in a draw\", \"failDescription\": \"You failed to defeat the opponent\", \"fleeDescription\": \"You fled from the opponent\", \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"attackers_chance\": 0, \"completionOutcome\": \"Win\", \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"opponent_scaled_to_user\": false, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"UP6j6slvyRS3oT3RYBwA1\", \"task\": \"defeat_opponents\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/eda185fa-fb67-497e-ac0e-f320c6fad04a-kpjdhk.webp\", \"sector\": 264, \"latitude\": 8, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 9, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"scaleGains\": 1, \"description\": \"\", \"opponent_ai\": \"SAZrjNFK30GatL9QsPZlN\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": false, \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"opponent_name\": \"Kaze no Seirei \", \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"drawDescription\": \"The battle ended in a draw\", \"failDescription\": \"You failed t