	('UuuubH6iXaD6bWsnwM3I8', 'Path of Hidden Blooms', 'https://utfs.io/f/6f4a1b46-5a28-49e6-b4de-ab138c1f2b04-17k.webp', '<p>Years ago, the renowned herbalist Datura mysteriously disappeared, leaving behind her abandoned shack and fragmented clues about her whereabouts.<br>Dusk, her former student, has spent years piecing together a riddle found within the ruins of her old home.<br>Now, with the riddle complete, Dusk seeks your aid.</p><br><br>\n\n<p><b>Dusk: \"Gathering these herbs will unlock the Celestial Teapot, a treasured relic of my master\'s.<br>Please, help me find them and together we may discover what became of her.<br>Keep in mind… she was always a trickster.\"</b></p><br><br>\n\nEight shadows creep beneath the blazing sun,<br>Three dunes hide what must be done.<br>Three scorching winds blow strong,<br>In this desert, find where it belongs.<br><br>Three kings once ruled these lofty skies,<br>Five winds blew where their legacy lies.<br>Four cliffs rise where the sage does grow,<br>Seek the isle where these numbers show.<br><br>Four blooms rise in a sunlit bed,<br>Five roots stretch deep where the light is shed.<br>Three petals guide the way,<br>In the desert’s heart, this flower stays.<br><br>Seven stars shine where the sea meets the land,<br>Four paths converge in the shimmering sand.<br>Two blossoms glow at night,<br>Find the peninsula where they shine their light.<br>~</p><br><br>\n\n<p>With the riddle and map in hand, your journey begins to uncover the secrets that lie ahead.</p><br>\n\n\n', '<p>As the sun sets, you return to Dusk with the Celestial Teapot. You give him the message from the kunoichi you encountered.<br>He chuckles to himself at your words and carefully opens the Teapot, revealing the hidden message from Datura inside.<br>After reading the message, a look of deep gratitude crosses his face. Both messages seem to fill Dusk with an anxious contentment.</p><br><br>\n\n<p><b>\"Thank you for this. I may finally find out what happened to her because of you.<br>Take this.<br>As you wear it, may it remind you of the journey you undertook and the flames of determination that burned bright within you.\"</b></p><br><br>\n\n<p>Together, you share the tea in silence, reflecting on the journey and the discovery, as the sun dips below the horizon.</p><br>\n', 'D', 1, NULL, 'all_time', 'event', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 1000, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [\"ufT6gjcDHcPShqEN0sVGv\"], \"reward_money\": 10000, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"reward_clanpoints\": 0}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"n6wLppZgMOtbUnJFVtcWH\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/6f4a1b46-5a28-49e6-b4de-ab138c1f2b04-17k.webp\", \"sector\": 453, \"latitude\": 5, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 5, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"Journey to the island where three kings once ruled. The cliffs are steep, and the winds are strong.<br>The Galecrest Sage grows high among the cliffs—find and gather this rare herb, braving the harsh elements.\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": true, \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"attackers_chance\": 0, \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"P4jJ_v1846kCrsBQmeDB7\", \"task\": \"collect_item\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/e6882e06-ee90-4e14-b43b-bd04b20ac23f-1d.webp\", \"sector\": 453, \"latitude\": 10, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"item_name\": \"Galecrest Sage\", \"longitude\": 10, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": true, \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"collect_item_id\": \"I6BenC2f5ETLp6BgDF_4v\", \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"attackers