	('X_B3axPFbeHaJKy7ZSKf4', 'The Scroll of Ascension', 'https://utfs.io/f/d7f5eb41-13b8-4591-9457-51706a6f78ea-hoq0lo.jpg', '<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/YjbaJAX.png\" alt=\"alt\">\n<p><center> Hiya! I’m Kokoga Kusha, your friendly neighborhood archaeologist, well, more like a scatterbrained seeker of lost secrets! So, here’s the thing, I’ve stumbled upon something pretty darn exciting, and I could really use a hand. You’ve heard of Hokori Satsume, right? The First Sage of Seichi. Well, I’ve got a hunch, a really good one, that I’ve found a clue leading to one of his legendary scrolls. I know, right?!</center></p><br>\n\n<p><center>The catch? The clue points straight to the Ironwood Forest, yep, that spooky, twisty, full-of-trouble place where ancient mysteries like to hide. I’m good at digging up the past, but, uh, not so great at dodging dangers that want to make me history. That’s where you come in! Think you could tag along and help a girl out? We’ve gotta snag this scroll before some baddie gets their hands on it.</center></p><br>\n\n<p><center>And get this, if it turns out to be the real deal, we could be looking at the fabled Scroll of Ascension! That’s the kind of thing that could unlock power so crazy big, it might just change the future of Seichi itself. No pressure or anything, but… what do you say? Ready to dive into some ancient chaos with me?</center></p><br>\n', 'You made it, yay!', 'D', 1, NULL, 'all_time', 'event', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 500, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [\"VvADyhc-xbzyP8Ovj9ZyE\"], \"reward_money\": 15000, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"reward_clanpoints\": 0}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"M5-ActYj1ZXUrX3X22QPB\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/d7f5eb41-13b8-4591-9457-51706a6f78ea-hoq0lo.jpg\", \"sector\": 307, \"latitude\": 2, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 4, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\