	('YSgv9Unnqu3687UO511Qn', 'The Path to Shroud', 'https://utfs.io/f/61b15090-818c-4885-b567-bd39bd1cc2b0-ayftz0.webp', 'Greetings, traveler. Shroud, a village blessed by Susanoo\'s storms, holds a rich history of resilience and divine intervention. To truly grasp the essence of this place, you must walk the path of the first settlers and experience the trials that transformed this barren land into a thriving haven. Join me in uncovering the story of Shroud.<br><br>\n\nBegin your journey at the Ravaged Sands, in a land seemingly forsaken by life. This desolate area was the initial settlement of the nomadic ninjas seeking a permanent home. Explore the sands that once reflected their desperation and unwavering faith.<br><br>\n\nNext, make your way to the Swamp of Sorrow. After Susanoo\'s initial response, the storms began to reshape the land. What seemed like a curse became a testament to their resilience.<br><br>\n\nContinue to the Savage Lakes, where the clan began to harness the power granted by Susanoo. This area reflects the strength and mastery over the elements they achieved. the clan found power and purpose. Their ability to control water and lightning marked a new beginning.<br><br>\n\nProceed to Spirit Lagoon, where the settlers began to see the storms not as a disaster but as a source of life and a symbol of divine favor.<br><br>\n\nFinally, A journey to the Misty Morass, the current site of Shroud. This is where Susanoo\'s blessing was fully realized, transforming the village into a haven shrouded in perpetual mists.\n', 'Congratulations, shinobi! You\'ve completed your mission in Shroud, revealing its rich history. Starting at the Ravaged Sands, you followed the path of the first settlers. In the Swamp of Sorrow, you saw resilience amidst storms. At Savage Lakes, you witnessed mastery over water and lightning. Spirit Lagoon showed storms as divine favor. Finally, in Misty Morass, you saw Shroud transformed into a mist-shrouded haven. Your dedication has honored Shroud\'s past. Well done! — Tenjiro Sensei', 'D', 1, NULL, 'all_time', 'event', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 0, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [\"WOZAR8VXUceHHTUMThzSu\"], \"reward_money\": 1000, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"reward_clanpoints\": 0}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"zMAUC_6BExQ5pwzDJaDZC\", \"task\": \"defeat_opponents\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/29bef02f-bee7-4c52-a1cb-1e36d61868b5-2wi7xh.webp\", \"sector\": 259, \"latitude\": 6, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 3, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"scaleGains\": 1, \"description\": \"\", \"opponent_ai\": \"adfgg3B6xMCtw5mf2FTxA\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": false, \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"opponent_name\": \"Sabaku no Yurei\", \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"drawDescription\": \"The battle ended in a draw\", \"failDescription\": \"You failed to defeat the opponent\", \"fleeDescription\": \"You fled from the opponent\", \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"attackers_chance\": 0, \"completionOutcome\": \"Win\", \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"opponent_scaled_to_user\": false, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"kCujw29LZGQMoK6euQX91\", \"task\": \"defeat_opponents\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/3308884f-5ccc-4a7a-ad81-cf7f27668b3e-1omb0r.webp\", \"sector\": 260, \"latitude\": 2, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 17, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"scaleGains\": 1, \"description\": \"\", \"opponent_ai\": \"9zteAgVlXWDTDzxSS4Jxm\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": false, \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"opponent_name\": \"Kappa Creature\", \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"drawDescription\": \"The battle ended in a draw\", \"failDescription\": \"You failed to defeat the opponent\", \"fleeDescription\": \"You fl